description:
Who doesn’t like robots? From factories to living rooms, robots are reshaping how we live and work. I’m excited to have partnered with Texas Instruments to explore how their tech is helping build smarter, safer, and more compact humanoid robots — like this one … meet Apollo!

To learn more about how @TexasInstruments technology and system-level solutions are helping design safer, smarter and more compact humanoid robots, visit https://bit.ly/4izOvfa
